    "description": {
      "value": "<h2><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 14pt;\">CAT BALANCE<br /></span></h2>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle1\" style=\"color: #000000;\">At 4</span><span class=\"fontstyle1\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 6pt;\">th </span><span class=\"fontstyle1\" style=\"color: #000000;\">level, you can increase one ability score of your choice by 1. You can&rsquo;t increase an ability score above 20 using this feature except for your primary runner ability, which has a maximum value of 22. </span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle1\" style=\"color: #000000;\">Additionally, your speed also increases by +5 feet.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle1\" style=\"color: #000000;\">Additionally, if you move at least 10 feet while moving towards a wall, your remaining movement becomes a climb speed until the end of your turn. This movement can be any direction as long as it follows a vertical surface.</span></p>",
